com.attributestudios.minecraft.installer.updates

Class UpdateFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.attributestudios.minecraft.installer.updates.UpdateFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UpdateConfigFile, UpdateModFile, UpdateResourceFile

    public abstract class UpdateFile
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Abstract class that represents the base of any type of updatable file related to a update. Includes strings used to identify a new and old file, a description string, an enum representing the action to be taken when installing this update, and the "side" to which this update should be installed.
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Bridger Maskrey (maskreybe@live.com)
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
    Date:
    2014-08-19
